===Noun===
'''yeast''' ([[uncountable]] and [[countable]]; plural: [[yeasts]])

# A type of single-celled [[fungus]].
# an often humid, yellowish [[froth]], made of these fungi, used in [[medicine]], in [[baking]] and in brewing [[beer]].
# A compressed cake or dried [[granule]]s of this substance used for mixing with flour to make bread dough rise.
# said of mental distress or agitation. <!--this sounds like an adjective-->
# (''figurative'') a frothy foam on sea waves.

